```

**Priority 3 - Code Reuse Refactoring** (Not blocking):
Extract the common late element handling to a helper method:
```java
protected void handleLateElement(StreamRecord<IN> element) {
    if (lateDataOutputTag != null) {
        sideOutput(element);
    } else {
        this.numLateRecordsDropped.inc();
